I"’<ol>
  <li>Download sources:
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>wget http://nginx.org/download/nginx-1.5.2.tar.gz <span class="nt">-O</span> - | <span class="nb">tar </span>zxf -
wget ftp://ftp.csx.cam.ac.uk/pub/software/programming/pcre/pcre-8.32.tar.gz <span class="nt">-O</span> - | <span class="nb">tar </span>zxf -
wget http://zlib.net/zlib-1.2.8.tar.gz <span class="nt">-O</span> - | <span class="nb">tar </span>zxf -
wget http://www.openssl.org/source/openssl-1.0.1e.tar.gz <span class="nt">-O</span> - | <span class="nb">tar </span>zxf -
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Build Nginx:
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">cd </span>nginx-1.5.2
./configure <span class="se">\</span>
  <span class="nt">--with-http_ssl_module</span> <span class="se">\</span>
  <span class="nt">--with-pcre</span><span class="o">=</span>../pcre-8.32 <span class="se">\</span>
  <span class="nt">--with-zlib</span><span class="o">=</span>../zlib-1.2.8 <span class="se">\</span>
  <span class="nt">--with-openssl</span><span class="o">=</span>../openssl-1.0.1e <span class="se">\</span>
  <span class="nt">--sbin-path</span><span class="o">=</span>/usr/bin <span class="se">\</span>
  <span class="nt">--conf-path</span><span class="o">=</span>/etc/nginx/nginx.conf <span class="se">\</span>
  <span class="nt">--with-ipv6</span> <span class="se">\</span>
  <span class="nt">--with-http_dav_module</span> 
   
make <span class="o">&amp;&amp;</span> make <span class="nb">install</span>
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
</ol>

